authorized servers (emails may be marked as spam but not rejected).\n\n### **SOA Record** (Start of Authority)\n```\nbart.ns.cloudflare.com. dns.cloudflare.com. 2392992790 10000 2400 604800 1800\n```\n\nContains zone management information:\n- Primary nameserver: `bart.ns.cloudflare.com`\n- Admin email: `dns@cloudflare.com`\n- Serial: `2392992790`\n- Refresh: 10000 seconds\n- Retry: 2400 seconds\n- Expire: 604800 seconds (7 days)\n- Minimum TTL: 1800 seconds\n\n**Summary:** This domain is hosted on Cloudflare with Google Workspace for email. The setup is standard and well-configured for a production environment."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1757,"cache_read_input_tokens":15275,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1757,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":757,"service_tier":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CWrzKUg7FhuVVqjzbG1hs","type":"assistant","uuid":"e9847208-f8bc-486b-949a-7a085e340a93","timestamp":"2026-01-06T23:26:16.968Z"}
